From: Even Rouault <even.rouault@mines-paris.org>
Date: Sat, 4 Nov 2017 11:29:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] XLSX/ODS: avoid using CPLSPrintf() return directly with
 VSIFOpenL() as the temp buffer might be later recycled. Fixes
 https://bugs.chromium.org/p/oss-fuzz/issues/detail?id=4050. Credit to OSS
 Fuzz

git-svn-id: https://svn.osgeo.org/gdal/trunk@40631 f0d54148-0727-0410-94bb-9a71ac55c965
