 .../ogrsf_frmts/xlsx/ogrxlsxdatasource.cpp    | 46 ++++++++++---------
 gdal/ogr/ogrsf_frmts/xlsx/ogrxlsxdriver.cpp   | 16 +++++--
 4 files changed, 50 insertions(+), 35 deletions(-)

